{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onload","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers\"><code>GlobalEventHandlers</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eigenschaften</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onerror\"><code>onerror</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/ongotpointercapture\"><code>ongotpointercapture</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><em><code>onload</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onloadeddata\"><code>onloadeddata</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onloadedmetadata\"><code>onloadedmetadata</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onloadend\"><code>onloadend</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onloadstart\"><code>onloadstart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onlostpointercapture\"><code>onlostpointercapture</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onpause\"><code>onpause</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onplay\"><code>onplay</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onplaying\"><code>onplaying</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\">Die <strong><code>onload</code></strong>-Eigenschaft der <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers\"><code>GlobalEventHandlers</code></a> ist ein Ereignis-Handler für das <code>load</code>-Ereignis eines <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a>s, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\"><code>XMLHttpRequest</code></a>s, <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/HTML/Element/img\"><code>&lt;img&gt;</code></a>-Elements, etc., der aufgerufen wird, wenn die Ressource fertig geladen hat.</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">window.onload = <em>funcRef</em>;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"value","title":"Value","isH3":true,"content":"<p><code>funcRef</code> ist die Handler-Funktion, die aufgerufen wird, wenn das <code>load</code>-Ereignis des Windows eintritt.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"beispiele","title":"Beispiele","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onload</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">init</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token function\">etwasAnderesTun</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token doctype\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;!</span><span class=\"token doctype-tag\">doctype</span> <span class=\"token name\">html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>onload-Test<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>title</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    // ES5\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">load</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"load-Ereignis festgestellt!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>onload <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> load<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    // ES2015\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">load</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"load-Ereignis festgestellt!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>onload <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> load<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>head</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Das load-Ereignis tritt ein, wenn das Dokument fertig geladen ist!<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>p</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"anmerkungen","title":"Anmerkungen","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Das <code>load</code>-Ereignis tritt am Ende des Dokumentladeprozesses ein. An diesem Punkt befinden sich alle Objekte des Dokuments im DOM und alle Grafiken, Skripte, Links und Sub-Frames sind vollständig geladen.</p>\n\n<p>Es gibt zudem <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/Events\">Gecko-spezifische DOM-Ereignisse</a> wie <code>DOMContentLoaded</code> und <code>DOMFrameContentLoaded</code> (welches mit <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\"><code>EventTarget.addEventListener()</code></a> gehandhabt werden kann), die eintreten, nachdem sich der DOM der Seite aufgebaut hat, aber nicht darauf warten, dass andere Ressourcen fertig geladen wurden.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Spezifikation</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Kommentar</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#handler-onload\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'onload' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Anfängliche Definition</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser-kompatibilität","title":"Browser-Kompatibilität","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect3\"><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect4\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Wir konvertieren die Kompatibilitätsdaten in ein maschinenlesbares JSON Format</a></strong>.\n            Diese Kompatibilitätstabelle liegt noch im alten Format vor,\n            denn die darin enthaltenen Daten wurden noch nicht konvertiert.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Finde heraus wie du helfen kannst! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect5\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Mobile</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div></div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari (WebKit)</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Android Webview</th>\n   <th>Edge</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Firefox OS</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n   <th>Chrome for Android</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Bitte mit der frühsten Version des Supports updaten.\">(Ja)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"siehe_auch","title":"Siehe auch","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code>DOMContentLoaded</code>-Ereignis in <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Listening_to_events_in_Firefox_extensions#Simple_DOM_events\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">Listening to events: Simple DOM events</a></li>\n <li>IIFE <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Immediately-invoked_function_expression\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external\">Immediately-invoked function expression</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Beispiele","id":"beispiele"},{"text":"Anmerkungen","id":"anmerkungen"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browser-Kompatibilität","id":"browser-kompatibilität"},{"text":"Siehe auch","id":"siehe_auch"}],"summary":"funcRef ist die Handler-Funktion, die aufgerufen wird, wenn das load-Ereignis des Windows eintritt.","popularity":0.0004,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"window.onload","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"window.onload","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"window.onload","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onload","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/globaleventhandlers/onload","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/globaleventhandlers/onload/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/de/docs/Web","title":"Webtechnologien für Entwickler"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API Referenz"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers","title":"GlobalEventHandlers"},{"uri":"/de/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/onload","title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onl